tweets.text:
@TheBodyShop @CrueltyFreeIntl #EU_REACH aims to ensure safe use of chemicals to protect people. Companies should use #AlternativesToAnimalTesting whenever possible.

To protect workers manufacturing cosmetics, safety tests are needed when there is no other way to demonstrate safe use.

https://t.co/VQClZV93GD

Harmful chemicals in products need to be tracked so they don’t end up in recycled materials ♻️.

If you produce, import or supply articles containing substances of very high concern, you need to notify 
@EU_ECHA from January 2021 onwards via the #SCIPDatabase.
